I am a teaching instructor for the following courses of the [MSc European Forestry](https://www.uef.fi/en/web/mdp-europeanforestry) (Erasmus Mundus MSc programme) at University of LLeida:

- ST in methods in hazard analysis and risk assessment [(111003)](http://guiadocent.udl.cat/pdf/pdf/en/111003.pdf)
- Introduction to spatial statistics with R [(111019)](Introduction to Spatial Statistics: Spatial analysis with R)
 
Former lecturer at the [MsC in Geographic Information Technologies](https://estudios.unizar.es/estudio/ver?id=608) - University of Zaragoza:

- Acquisiton and Organization of Geographic Information [(60401)](https://estudios.unizar.es/estudio/asignatura?anyo_academico=2018&asignatura_id=60401&estudio_id=20180608&centro_id=103&plan_id_nk=352)
- Geographic Information Analysis: Geographic Information Systems [(60402)](https://sia.unizar.es/doa/consultaPublica/look[conpub]MostrarPubGuiaDocAs?entradaPublica=true&idiomaPais=es.ES&_anoAcademico=2018&_codAsignatura=60402)
- Thematic Cartography, Geovisualization and Web Mapping [(60418)](https://sia.unizar.es/doa/consultaPublica/look[conpub]MostrarPubGuiaDocAs?entradaPublica=true&idiomaPais=es.ES&_anoAcademico=2018&_codAsignatura=60418)
